Good.

6
00:00:28,830 --> 00:00:30,390
We're a family.

7
00:00:30,510 --> 00:00:32,030
Spare the formalities.

8
00:00:32,030 --> 00:00:33,000
Qingxia,

9
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:35,280
it's time for you
to address me differently.

10
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:36,710
Alright, Father.

11
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:38,030
Hahaha.

12
00:00:38,030 --> 00:00:39,110
Have a seat.

13
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,390
Housekeeper.

14
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,320
Our guests have sent you two many gifts

15
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:53,110
