16
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:53,560
I picked

17
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:55,670
two of the more unique gifts.

18
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,240
I'm going to show them to you guys.

19
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,640
This pair of earrings
has a history behind them.

20
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:03,280
The person who gifted the earrings

21
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:05,710
