by a famous western designer.

22
00:01:05,710 --> 00:01:06,350
Hahaha.

23
00:01:06,590 --> 00:01:08,640
Once Nie Zhen takes over my position
as the Grand Marshal,

24
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:09,430
this pair of earrings

25
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,310
will fit you well.

26
00:01:15,070 --> 00:01:15,870
This is

27
00:01:16,350 --> 00:01:17,560
for you.

28
