I don't like it.

29
00:01:24,070 --> 00:01:25,150
Listen up.

30
00:01:26,070 --> 00:01:27,640
You're going to be
a grand marshal eventually.

31
00:01:27,710 --> 00:01:29,120
You have to like firearms
regardless of what you think.

32
00:01:29,150 --> 00:01:29,950
Father,

33
00:01:29,950 --> 00:01:31,480
it's mealtime.

34
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:33,280
There's no need for you
to show us this gift

35
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,640
