36
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,710
Hmph.

37
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,710
What do you mean by that?

38
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:40,590
Thank you, Father.

39
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,040
I love the gift.

40
00:01:42,790 --> 00:01:43,590
Ah.

41
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,000
What about this?

42
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,480
I'll keep this gun

43
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,280
in my room.

44
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:54,590
I'll give it to the brat

45
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,200
during next year's
inauguration ceremony.

46
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,350
Alright.

47
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:01,920
What's wrong?

48
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,000
You were afraid of me before this.

49
