I'm an orphan.

59
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,150
I was abandoned since I was young.

60
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:35,590
I want you to help locate
my biological parents.

61
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,430
That's simple.

62
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:38,680
But it takes time.

63
