I've been waiting for 20 years.

64
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,430
Waiting a little longer doesn't matter.

65
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:49,280
Didn't you say you have
official matters to handle today?

66
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:50,430
You should go.

67
