Bang.

72
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:36,800
This is a warning.

73
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,520
You'll be punished

74
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:40,240
if you dare to shoot me again.

75
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:45,710
Finish the task as soon as possible.

76
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:47,190
Young Marshal,
are you in a hurry to return home?

77
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:48,560
That's right.

78
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,800
Did something happen?

79
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,400
It's nothing.

80
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,840
I'm just homesick.

81
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,800
You're homesick?

82
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:55,360
But we just left your house.

83
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,030
Don't be a smart alec.

84
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:06,590
[Le Grand Meaulnes]

85
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:12,870
Housekeeper.

86
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:14,240
Young Madam.

87
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,240
Do you need anything?

88
