Is Father around?

89
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,480
Oh, unfortunately,

90
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,800
the Grand Marshal went to the
division headquarters right after lunch.

91
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,800
He'll only return home
tomorrow night at the earliest.

92
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:25,360
Young Madam, you can tell me
if you need anything.

93
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:26,920
