the situation to me then?

143
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,240
Why was she sneaking around

144
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,070
Grand Marshal's room then?

145
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,510
Young Madam was just trying to...

146
