You have no right to speak here.

147
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,510
Stop bullying him.

148
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,720
Mistress Nie,
I already explained myself to you.

149
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,920
I was delivering a Chinese medicine
prescription to the Grand Marshal's room.

150
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,070
Nonsense!

151
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:03,920
Do you think Qingxia
needs your permission

152
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,070
to enter my father's room?

153
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,430
That's not what I mean.

154
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:10,600
But I knew that she was
definitely up to no good,

155
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,480
judging from the way she acted.

156
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,190
Nie Zhen,

157
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,120
this happened

158
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:19,360
because I wasn't considerate enough.

159
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,480
That's right.

160
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,000
Nie Ping should be

161
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,310
the judge here.

162
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,510
At least you can't make the call here.

163
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,830
What are you doing?

164
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:56,020
♪If the past can be relived♪

165
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:58,420
♪Time would be haggard♪

166
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:03,900
♪Destiny is the consolation you provide♪

167
